videos.description: On the opening kickoff, Jerry Howard struggles to locate the ball and decides to run it out of the end zone and is tackled at his own 1-yard line.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech off to a rough start

videos.description: Georgia's Nick Chubb recieves the handoff and runs the ball up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bulldogs on the board first with easy TD

videos.description: QB Javon Wims finds Jake Fromm in the end zone for another Georgia touchdown.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' QB throws a laser for TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Nathan Cottrell receives the pitch and runs down the edge of the sideline for a 33-yard run.
videos.headline: Yellow Jackets' Cottrell tightropes down sideline

videos.description: QB Ricky Jeune finds TaQuon Marshall wide open in the end zone for a Yellow Jackets' touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech cuts the lead in half with easy TD

videos.description: Georgia head coach Kirby Smart talks about the miscommunication on Georgia Tech's touchdown and his offense's production.
videos.headline: Smart discusses first-half frustrations

videos.description: Georgia Tech head coach Paul Johnson shares his message to his team during halftime, and how they need to get more stops.
videos.headline: Johnson wants more stops from D

videos.description: Jake Fromm throws deep to Mecole Hardman for 39 yards with a defender wrapped around him, putting Georgia in the red zone.
videos.headline: Great catch by Bulldogs' Hardman

videos.description: Bulldogs' Sony Michel breaks some ankles, as he jukes out Yellow Jacket defenders for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia's Michel zigzags into the end zone

videos.description: D'Andre Swift sprints down the sidelines and reaches for the pylon, putting the Bulldogs in scoring position.
videos.headline: Swift's 31-yard run puts Georgia in red zone

videos.description: D'Andre Swift flips over a pile of players, extending Georgia's lead.
videos.headline: Swift leaps over defenders for a Bulldog TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech's TaQuon Marshall's pass is intercepted in the end zone by Georgia's Deandre Baker, who returns it for 15 yards.
videos.headline: Yellow Jackets QB throws interception

videos.description: Georgia's Jake Fromm launches the ball under pressure and finds Ahkil Crumpton for a 78-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Fromm makes incredible throw for 78-yard Bulldogs TD

videos.description: ESPN's Greg McElroy and Dave Pasch breakdown Georgia's dominant win and highlight the Bulldogs' backfield.
videos.headline: Bulldogs roll over the Yellow Jackets
